Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是突然出现的异形军团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则正打算终结这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义勇军的 尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉娜 用恢复魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 只是昏过去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:50.30,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1560,890)\blur2}共存之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙 打算返回副都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的人大家都很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没什么大不了的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 是尤里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你是义勇军的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是菲娜 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把风的凯恩他们也差不多要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 凯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 请尽情大吃特吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能吃得下菲娜做的菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呀 不是超级好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 平常都吃些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了 请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多很多尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你不是那个村庄的住民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路过而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算以一己之力保护那个村庄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能见死不救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也看不惯那些黑漆漆的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真是强大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我还不够强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想变得更加 更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜小姐 锁链编年史它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是 锁链编年史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记录了世间所有的年代记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界染上了黑暗之时 锁链编年史也会被染黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反之同理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有 好多页被染黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗蔓延的越来越广了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精的下落还没查到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不是在上次的战斗中抹杀掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界还没有真的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 比利卡还活在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的伙伴 一个小妖精哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点毒舌 但是对这个世界来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡代表着世界所期待的未来的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须找出比利卡 把她解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找出并杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那个妖精还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界就不会完结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们稍稍谈谈可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你为什么追求强大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是因为弱小的家伙什么也做不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 加入我们和我们一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我是不会参加义勇军的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人更加自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的战斗总是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止我也是一个人战斗着过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也不是从没有输过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有过从赢不了的对手面前逃走的经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后会成长到能打赢他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是运气好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底知道我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算是有同伴在也输了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方的路 好像没有受到影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天一亮我们就出发吧 回副都去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让那些家伙继续涌进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够 还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的武器 可全是好货哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们回来了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战况现在如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南方的桥梁已经沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外牆正如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平民区城牆的情况由雅露朵拉在奋战 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新人吗 气势不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去支援雅露朵拉她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人数量众多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一口气上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又夺取我的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布尔克哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再找你算帐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 刚才那招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是我们的联合攻击招式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过重叠招式威力大幅提高了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这需要大家魔力的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你现在还做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要刻苦练习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 这个不是简单就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个招式需要的是强大的羁绊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就不知道什么是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是纯粹地按自己的想法擅自行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有我自己的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是在说那是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚 但你竟然能夺取我的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那点事 又怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是不能干涉他人魔力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无知也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做不到就嘲讽别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你这样的野狗讲道理也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是喜欢才跟你们混在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话我走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己会以我的方法变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要去追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那种家伙任意妄为 破坏纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道没有发觉这样的天真会让你变得懦弱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得阿兰姆大有潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才一直带他来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能成为一个好战士的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 正主登场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这个雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾越来越浓了 这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会保护尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑之王打败的我 迷失了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 看着你在那个村庄拼命奋战的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回想起了我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓无论发生什么也绝不放弃的过去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我才不管呢 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我找回自我的时候 我的身边有我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有丢弃我继续支撑着我的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人无法克服的困难 和同伴一起就能克服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是羁绊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你确实很强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用魔力的天赋比谁都敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果你也拥有羁绊的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能变得比现在更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我并肩作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经快要支撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下请退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布尔克哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才借的份可都还给你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布尔克哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束战局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们好好见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 他也相当能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 回来的正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得再陪你们一会儿也没关系罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想再多看看你的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 被那家伙这样说我可是很不爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样也没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话想对大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾败于黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之王曾说 世界终将走向灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算如此 我也不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要活着就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想再集结一次黑之王讨伐队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨伐队 那可不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要从大陆集结力量 组成讨伐军才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里满血复活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我认同的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在得意个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿兰姆 你的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就认同他吧 他不是也把魔力还给你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下先退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布尔克哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布尔克哈特
